      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了，检查一下：IngressController下面有docs和blog两个负载均衡器，EtcdCluster下面挂着RedisCache。层级关系对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
